@Deprecated public class UserMessageYesterdayBar extends Object implements velox.api.layer1.messages.Layer1ApiIgnorableUpwardMessage

Deprecated: not used in current versions of bookmap, will likely be removed from API later. Encapsulates yesterday bar information - contract name and OLHC prices.
